snippet: Alfonzo Dennard was arrested and accused of driving drunk in Lincoln, Neb., where he once starred as a defensive back for the Cornhuskers.
abstract: New England Patriots defensive back Alfonzo Dennard is arrested and charged with drunk driving in Lincoln, Neb.
lead_paragraph: Alfonzo Dennard was arrested and accused of driving drunk in Lincoln, Neb., where he once starred as a defensive back for the Cornhuskers.

headline.main: Patriots’ Dennard Is Accused of Driving Drunk
